##Wuhan woman Doctor Xiasi left, Father's circle of friends to write a paragraph

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

The following article is from Chutian metropolis daily, written by Liu Xun

Chutian metropolis daily, Hubei Circulation, user volume, the most influential media, every day to give you the most fresh, the most practical, the most fun information.

Chutian metropolis daily

The 23rd,

Wuhan Xiehe Jiangbei Hospital Officials micro-announcement,

The mourning begins at 6:30 this morning

The unfortunate Dr. Shays.

The full text of the announcement is as follows:

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
HUSBAND: The wife is infected and wants to recover with him on the line

At noon today, Chutian metropolis daily reporter contacted Xia SI's husband, Wu Shilei, an Orthopedist at Puai Hospital in Wuhan.

"She left without a word, " he sobbed.

Shays, 29, a resident in the Department of Gastroenterology at Union Jiangbei District Hospital, contracted the infection while treating patients.

On January 15, a 70-year-old man in our department became seriously ill and found abnormal CT findings in his lungs. That day, Shaisi just off night shift, after the shift ready to go home, temporary received the task, they inform her husband to change the itinerary, return to the hospital to participate in treatment, coordination expert consultation, Inspection. In the next few days, Shaisi worried about the old man's illness, actively stay in the ward.

I didn't know I was infected, despite all the precautions. On January 19, she suddenly developed a high fever, after examination, found the lung CT ground glass shadow changes, highly suspected, then in the Concord Jiangbei Hospital isolation treatment.

"At the beginning, the condition was relatively stable, and we also discussed that when she recovered, we would be on the front line together. " Wu Shilei choked up, and in the middle of the night of February 7, his wife suddenly became sicker, breathing, cardiac arrest, and overnight rescue was organized by the hospital. Although her life was saved, but people are in comas all the time, and oxygen saturation is low.

The group decided to start with ECMO and immediately transfer to Zhongnan Hospital of Wuhan University. In the ICU, hiss condition blood pressure fluctuations, the major hospital experts are in its way. However, at 6:30 this morning, he died in vain.
2-year-old son still thinks MOM's at work

Wu Shilei said that the two university medical students, in the most beautiful campus to meet, love, experienced many difficulties together, has gone through 11 years.

"She also suffered a lot for our family, " said Wu Shilei, whose wife broke the water when she was 23 weeks pregnant and kept the fetus motionless for more than 10 days. At 30 weeks, she suddenly developed a fever and gave birth to a son by Caesarean section. The baby was only three pounds, two ounces, spent a lot of time in the cooler.

"It's hard to feed a premature baby, and my family has barely slept through two years, " he said.
Last November, in order to repay the elderly, Xiasi use annual leave, with both sides of the elderly, the family for the first time neatly to Sanya holiday..

"I never thought this would be the last time. "

"The baby was born prematurely, and I haven't been able to return to my hometown for more than two years, so I can show it to my grandparents, " said Wu, who bought tickets for the New Year but had to postpone them because of the epidemic. We thought we'd get together with the old people when the epidemic was over, but..."

While his wife was in the hospital, the family lied to their children and lied to their mother about going to work. Wu Shilei said, as long as the phone rings, the Son Will Rob to call his mother, now his wife left, he did not know how to explain to the child.

My father was so distraught that he wrote this to his friends

Shaith's father was grief-stricken. Write this on facebook:

"Dear Siz, at 6:50 this morning, you are 29 years, 9 months and 20 days old, away from your sweet 2-year-old son, your loving husband, your loving parents and loved ones, your loving medical career and the patients who depend on you. Baby girl, you go well and be happy in heaven. Dear daughter, we will always love you, always miss you! As I always loved your father, 23 February 2020

Good Luck, beautiful angel!
